summary: Just like the text part of this image collection says. Things are tight. I’ve got a few different backup plans so I’m not going...
caption:
Just like the text part of this image collection says. Things are tight. I’ve got a few different backup plans so I’m not going to end up on the street but any help I can get either commissions, donations, or strong leads on single rooms for a one month lease in Los Angeles the better off I’ll be. I have plans to move into a long term lease with some friends but I need to buy myself at least a month because their lease isn’t up yet and I’m a little stranded. 

I included some of my recent work and commissions above! 
(Featured characters belong to @crocodilecrayons , LoriLUNACY and Schonheit on Deviantart, @lizkay , @kbearart , and @regal-reindeer . The last two are closed species characters I designed. Esks belong to Witherlings on DA, Grems belong to MrGremble on DA. 

Inquire about commissions at my email! Just note that I won’t be starting any new commissions until I have my computer set up again after I move but I’m more than happy to answer questions, give you a quote, or add you to my queue.  

Sarspax@gmail.com

Current Commission info (wip)

https://www.deviantart.com/sarspax/art/Commission-Catalog-v2-WIP-735438522

https://www.deviantart.com/sarspax/art/Commission-Catalog-v2-WIP-735438522

https://www.deviantart.com/sarspax/art/Commission-Catalog-v2-WIP-735438522

My Ko-Fi is open for Pay-What-You-Want sketches. What I sketch is time based at $1 per minute (the same rate as my $30 for 30 min sketches I use to do a lot). 

https://ko-fi.com/sarspax

https://ko-fi.com/sarspax

https://ko-fi.com/sarspax

Regardless on which of my plans/backup plans I have to go with I’ll have my desktop computer set up again in a week at the latest. Until then I’m limited to sketches on my tablet. 

I also have a bunch of adopts for sale still: 

https://sarspax.tumblr.com/post/176668278764/sarspax-a-handful-of-people-were-interested-in

https://sarspax.tumblr.com/post/176636214694/sarspax-sarspax-money-is-really-tight-right

summary: Pretty rare for me to share my unfinished pencil work here, but I liked these. [[MORE]] The lovely old apex lady is Aly,...
caption:
Pretty rare for me to share my unfinished pencil work here, but I liked these. 

The lovely old apex lady is Aly, rebellion’s resident grandma and still a respectable sword-master even at her age. She went toe to toe with Aram in their youth and won. The novakid is Azen Luko, a floran-raised vigilante, and also Isobu’s mentor. She’s a blue giant now at an impressive 600 years old, mostly-quietly retired from the crime fighting life. And because I can, snuggle-ball of Vasim and Kyo~ Lookit his lil’ toe beans
